# 🍱 TiffinConnect — Full Application Overview

## 1. What is TiffinConnect?

TiffinConnect is a **full-stack SaaS meal-delivery subscription platform** built for the Indian market. It connects:
- **Customers** who want daily home-cooked tiffin deliveries (lunch/dinner)
- **Vendors (Tiffin Providers)** who cook and list meals
- **Admins** who manage the platform, approve vendors, and monitor orders

---

## 2. Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| **Framework** | React 18 + Vite (TypeScript) |
| **Routing** | React Router DOM v6 |
| **UI Components** | Radix UI + shadcn/ui |
| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS v3 + custom CSS animations |
| **Animations** | Framer Motion |
| **Backend / DB** | Supabase (PostgreSQL + RLS + Auth) |
| **State Management** | TanStack React Query v5 |
| **Forms** | React Hook Form + Zod |
| **Payments** | Razorpay (integrated) |
| **Toast Notifications** | Sonner + Radix Toast |
| **Icons** | Lucide React |
| **Charts** | Recharts |
| **Date Utilities** | date-fns |

---

## 3. Project Root Structure

```
tiffin-connect-hub-59/
├── src/
│   ├── App.tsx              ← Root router & providers
│   ├── main.tsx             ← React entry point
│   ├── index.css            ← Global CSS + design tokens
│   ├── components/          ← Shared layout & UI components
│   ├── pages/               ← All page components
│   ├── hooks/               ← Custom hooks (auth, toast, mobile)
│   ├── integrations/        ← Supabase client
│   └── lib/                 ← Utility functions
├── supabase/
│   ├── config.toml
│   └── migrations/          ← SQL schema files
├── .env                     ← Supabase credentials
├── tailwind.config.ts
└── package.json
```

