## 4. Authentication & Role System

### Auth Provider ([src/hooks/useAuth.tsx](file:///e:/DELTA/M%20A%20I%20N%20M%20A%20I%20N/FULL%20STACK%20DEPLOYES%20PROJECTS/TiffinConnect/tiffin-connect-hub-59/src/hooks/useAuth.tsx))
- Uses **Supabase Auth** (`signInWithPassword`, `signUp`, `onAuthStateChange`)
- Maintains global state: `user`, `session`, `role`, `loading`
- On login, fetches the user's `app_role` from the `user_roles` table
- Roles: `"user"` | `"vendor"` | `"admin"`

### Protected Route ([src/components/ProtectedRoute.tsx](file:///e:/DELTA/M%20A%20I%20N%20M%20A%20I%20N/FULL%20STACK%20DEPLOYES%20PROJECTS/TiffinConnect/tiffin-connect-hub-59/src/components/ProtectedRoute.tsx))
- Wraps dashboard routes
- If not logged in → redirects to `/login`
- If wrong role → redirects to correct dashboard
- While loading → shows animated loading screen

### Role-Based Dashboard Routing
| Role | Dashboard URL |
|---|---|
| `user` | `/dashboard/*` → [UserDashboard](file:///e:/DELTA/M%20A%20I%20N%20M%20A%20I%20N/FULL%20STACK%20DEPLOYES%20PROJECTS/TiffinConnect/tiffin-connect-hub-59/src/pages/UserDashboard.tsx#28-53) |
| `vendor` | `/vendor/*` → [VendorDashboard](file:///e:/DELTA/M%20A%20I%20N%20M%20A%20I%20N/FULL%20STACK%20DEPLOYES%20PROJECTS/TiffinConnect/tiffin-connect-hub-59/src/pages/VendorDashboard.tsx#25-50) |
| `admin` | `/admin/*` → [AdminDashboard](file:///e:/DELTA/M%20A%20I%20N%20M%20A%20I%20N/FULL%20STACK%20DEPLOYES%20PROJECTS/TiffinConnect/tiffin-connect-hub-59/src/pages/AdminDashboard.tsx#25-50) |

