- Lists available menus from approved vendors
- Users can subscribe to a meal plan

### [SubscriptionPage](file:///e:/DELTA/M%20A%20I%20N%20M%20A%20I%20N/FULL%20STACK%20DEPLOYES%20PROJECTS/TiffinConnect/tiffin-connect-hub-59/src/pages/dashboard/SubscriptionPage.tsx#11-174)
- Lists all subscriptions for the logged-in user
- Actions: **Pause**, **Resume**, **Cancel** subscriptions
