## 11. Database Schema (Supabase / PostgreSQL)

### Tables

| Table | Key Columns | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `profiles` | `user_id`, `full_name`, `phone`, `avatar_url` | User profile data |
| `user_roles` | `user_id`, `role (enum)` | Role assignment (user/vendor/admin) |
| `addresses` | `user_id`, `label`, `address_line`, `city`, `state`, `pincode`, `lat/lng`, `is_default` | Delivery addresses |
| `vendors` | `user_id`, `business_name`, `description`, `delivery_radius_km`, `is_approved`, `is_active` | Vendor profiles |
| `menus` | `vendor_id`, `name`, `meal_type`, `price`, `items (JSONB)`, `is_available` | Meal menus |
| `subscriptions` | `user_id`, `vendor_id`, `menu_id`, `plan_type`, `meal_type`, [status](file:///e:/DELTA/M%20A%20I%20N%20M%20A%20I%20N/FULL%20STACK%20DEPLOYES%20PROJECTS/TiffinConnect/tiffin-connect-hub-59/src/pages/dashboard/SubscriptionPage.tsx#45-53), `start_date`, `end_date`, `amount` | User subscriptions |
| `orders` | `user_id`, `vendor_id`, `subscription_id`, `meal_type`, `delivery_date`, [status](file:///e:/DELTA/M%20A%20I%20N%20M%20A%20I%20N/FULL%20STACK%20DEPLOYES%20PROJECTS/TiffinConnect/tiffin-connect-hub-59/src/pages/dashboard/SubscriptionPage.tsx#45-53), `amount` | Individual delivery orders |
| `payments` | `user_id`, `order_id`, `subscription_id`, `razorpay_*`, `amount`, [status](file:///e:/DELTA/M%20A%20I%20N%20M%20A%20I%20N/FULL%20STACK%20DEPLOYES%20PROJECTS/TiffinConnect/tiffin-connect-hub-59/src/pages/dashboard/SubscriptionPage.tsx#45-53) | Payment records (Razorpay) |

### Row Level Security (RLS)
- All tables have RLS enabled
- Users only see/edit their own data
- Vendors see subscriptions and orders for their business
- Admins have full access via `has_role()` security definer function
- Auto-trigger `handle_new_user()` creates profile + role on signup

### Enums & Constraints
- `app_role`: `user | vendor | admin`
- `plan_type`: `daily | weekly | monthly`
- `meal_type`: `lunch | dinner | both`
- `order status`: `pending | confirmed | preparing | out_for_delivery | delivered | cancelled`
- `subscription status`: `active | paused | cancelled | expired`
- `payment status`: `created | authorized | captured | failed | refunded`

---

## 12. Integrations

### Supabase (`src/integrations/supabase/client.ts`)
- Client initialized with `VITE_SUPABASE_URL` and `VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY`
- Used across all pages for DB queries, auth, and real-time

### Razorpay
- Payment flow integrated (Razorpay script loaded externally)
- Payment IDs stored in the `payments` table (`razorpay_order_id`, `razorpay_payment_id`, `razorpay_signature`)
- Webhook integration for purchase confirmation emails

---

## 13. Key Design Patterns

- **TanStack React Query** for all server state (caching, refetching, mutations)
- **Optimistic UI** via `queryClient.invalidateQueries` on mutations
- **Framer Motion** for smooth staggered animations and hover/tap interactions
- **Glassmorphism** design system (custom CSS classes: `glass`, `glass-card`, `glass-subtle`)
- **Sonner toasts** for all success/error feedback
- **Responsive layouts** — all pages are mobile-friendly
- **Dark/Light mode** — `ThemeToggle` in both Navbar and sidebar

---

## 14. Pricing Plans (Landing Page)

| Plan | Price | Features |
|---|---|---|
| Daily | ₹80/meal | Single meal, pay per order |
| Weekly ⭐ | ₹499/week | Lunch + Dinner, priority delivery, 10% savings |
| Monthly | ₹1,799/month | Full plan, 25%, pause anytime, dedicated chef |

